<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>For Putri ❤️</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

</head>

<body>

<!-- MUSIC -->

<audio id="bgMusic" loop>
<source src="music.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

<!-- LOADING -->

<div id="loading-screen">

<div class="loading-content">

<h1>For Putri ❤️</h1>

<p>Loading memories...</p>

<div class="loader"></div>

</div>

</div>

<!-- SAKURA -->

<div id="petals-container"></div>

<!-- HERO -->

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-overlay"></div>

<div class="hero-content">

<h1>Putri Handayani ❤️</h1>

<p class="subtitle">

A little place made from my heart

</p>

<img src="foto1.jpg" class="hero-image">

<button id="startBtn">

💌 Open My Heart

</button>

</div>

</section>

<!-- ENVELOPE -->

<section id="envelope-section" class="hidden">

<div class="envelope-wrapper">

<div class="envelope">

<div class="letter">

<h2>For You ❤️</h2>

<p>

Click the letter below

</p>

<button id="openLetter">

Read My Letter 💌

</button>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- LETTER -->

<section id="letter-section" class="hidden">

<div class="glass-card">

<h2>From My Heart ❤️</h2>

<p id="typingText"></p>

</div>

</section>

<!-- DAYS COUNTER -->

<section class="counter-section hidden">

<div class="counter-card">

<h2>Our Journey ❤️</h2>

<h1 id="daysCounter"></h1>

<p>Together and counting...</p>

</div>

</section>

<!-- GALLERY -->

<section class="gallery-section hidden">

<h2>Our Memories 📸</h2>

<div class="gallery">

<div class="slide">

<img src="foto1.jpg">

</div>

<div class="slide">

<img src="foto2.jpg">

</div>

<div class="slide">

<img src="foto3.jpg">

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- LOVE MESSAGE -->

<section class="love-section hidden">

<div class="love-card">

<h2>For My Favorite Person ❤️</h2>

<p>

Thank you for being part of my life.

Thank you for every laugh,

every conversation,

every memory,

and every moment we spend together.

You make ordinary days feel special.

And if I could choose again,

I would still choose you.

Every single time.

❤️

</p>

</div>

</section>

<!-- FINAL -->

<section class="final-section hidden">

<h1>I Love You ❤️</h1>

<p>

Forever isn't enough with you.

</p>

<button id="loveButton">

❤️ Click Me ❤️

</button>

</section>

<!-- CONFETTI -->

<canvas id="confetti"></canvas>

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>

</html>
